Text:
Can someone tell me what this show is about. It's too new to have anything about it online. At least that I can find.

Thank you

Classification: Reality
Genre: Horror/Supernatural
Status: New Series
Network: Syfy ( USA)
Airs: Wednesdays at 10:00 pm
Runtime: 60 Minutes
Premiere: February 27, 2013
Episode Order: 6

an all-new six-episode reality series that documents an unconventional – and terrifying – paranormal and psychological experiment. Each hour-long episode features the self-recorded footage of a diverse group of every-day paranormal enthusiasts - from newlyweds and a brother-in-law to a trio of roommates. Each team of three will be stranded at one of the most haunted locations in America and record the entire experience with hand-held cameras.
